album.title: The Complete Ella Fitzgerald Song Books

wiki.content:
"I Get a Kick Out of You" is a song by Cole Porter, originally featured in Anything Goes (1934).
 
 Originally sung by Ethel Merman, it has been covered by performers including Frank Sinatra, Billie Holiday, Marlene Dietrich, Cesare Siepi, Dinah Washington, Bobby Short, Louis Armstrong, Ella Fitzgerald, Mary Martin, Anita O`Day, Rosemary Clooney, Django Reinhardt, Gary Shearston, Jamie Cullum, The Living End, Dolly Parton, Dwele, Joan Morris, Shirley Bassey, and Lisa Ekdahl
 
 -Wikipedia
